{"tid":1323824,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"書展嗰時呢 如果見到有興趣嘅書","createTime":"2019-07-16T11:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T11:46:46.000Z","uid":225916,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1c4671756df9d00b4842cac17af2ca89ad44e434","tid":1323824,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:21:54.000Z","msg":"一定要攞嚟睇睇先<br />\n但打開咗之後 千祈唔好<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔記得cum返埋啲書</span></span><br />\n或者打算買 攞起好幾本書嗰時呢<br />\n都千祈唔好<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亂咁放埋一邊 唔記得咗放咗去邊呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係啲<span style=\"color: red;\">店員好慘架</span><br />\n仲會<span style=\"color: red;\">影響啲生意額</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到個場變垃圾堆咁樣就唔好啦<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊諗下仲有冇其他咩事 一定要記得？？"},{"pid":"fb0ba5a7f7efbbdf159028a237958b2b4cbf2b9f","tid":1323824,"uid":259901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:26:48.000Z","msg":"唔好咁啦<br />\n應該拎埋本書去問價先，之後再擺返好佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ec1efef28c6feebf778d867c7793e851a43758","tid":1323824,"uid":13349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:29:49.000Z","msg":"睇唔晒記得用書簽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d093a73bd2949492a2e7b3e1845a5fc49bff3d","tid":1323824,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}